title: Dutch people when it rains
description:
Scenes from the city of Utrecht in the Netherlands on a rainy day. Surprise, surprise, the rain does not stop Dutch people from going out and living their lives. Going about your day like nothing has changed when it rains is really just part of Dutch culture. Something I had to get used to as an American because in the United States cancelling plans because it's raining is quite understandable. 

Dutch people will always say, "you're not made of sugar" and my reaction to the rain sometimes really makes me wonder whether I might in fact indeed be made of sugar.
